                <h1>Embrace Windows 10 Dark Mode: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>Windows 10 Dark Mode is a sleek feature that transforms your interface to a darker color scheme, reducing eye strain and enhancing visual comfort, especially in low-light environments. To enable it, navigate to Settings > Personalization > Colors and choose "Dark." Enjoy a modern aesthetic while using your device!</p>
